title: Relation Theory
info:
Relation Theory
a co-op tune between Chuck Biscuits and Ozone

Originally finished in september 1995 for a Heretics intro called "Two" and released in october 1996 under the Kosmic Free Music Foundation.
Tested fine in IT, CapaMod and Mod4Win. DO NOT PLAY in Cubic!: the volume slides are completely incorrect.

25.10.96
